(newid(), 'http://localhost/projectinsight.webapp/api/help/model/itembase', '

PI® Web API

Help Page Home

ItemBase

The ItemBase class is the base class for all items in Project Insight. All items (Projects\, Tasks\, Folders\, Files\, etc) inherit from the ItemBase class. The ItemBase class contains the business logic and properties which are common to all items in the system including permissions\, the item name\, description\, child items parent items and more. The ItemBase object handles the business logic and data access for the specialized business object\, ItemBase. The class inherits from BusinessObjectBase class.

NameDescriptionType
ActivatedDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the NullableDateTime the item was activated. NullableDateTime
Admin Gets the string empty string\, used for the column selectors to obtain the name of the admin field. string

ApprovalRequestsLinks Gets the string list of comma separated approval request linked string
ApprovalRequestsString Gets the string list of comma separated approval requests string
ChangedPropertyValues Collection of PropertyChanged

Color Gets or sets the string color for the item. string

ConnectionString string

CopiedFromTmp BusinessObjectBase
CreatedAge Gets the Age object for the date created date. Age
CreatedDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the date created date time in universal time. date
CustomFieldSet Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.CustomFieldSet used for the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.CustomFieldValue if the item is a custom item. CustomFieldSet

Remarks: Default Property

 CustomFieldValue

DeadlockSleepMilliSecondsForSave integer
DefaultTableColumnSetKeyForFolderView Gets or sets the string string

DisplayType Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.DisplayType type of display. (Default "Tree"). DisplayType
Domain Gets the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.Domain this item is located on. This property is new added as of (2007-12-03) Domain
DomainId Gets or sets the guid Id of the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.Domain this item is located in. Set programmatically when an item is created as a child to another. Do not set manually. guid
DomainIntegrationExternalObjectsAreLoaded Gets the boolean flag indicating whether or not domain integration external objects have been loaded. (Used for save optimization on items) boolean
Event Gets the Event that the item is contained within (if any\, null otherwise). Event
ExternalCreatedBy Gets or sets the string external user who created the item string
ExternalDownloadUrl Gets or sets the string external preview URL string
ExternalId Gets or sets the string external ID for this item string
ExternalIntegrationService Gets the RestServiceBase that is responsible for this handeling external operations on this ItemBase. RestServiceBase
ExternalPreviewUrl Gets or sets the string external preview URL string
ExternalSyncByUser Gets or sets the NullableDateTime the item was last synched User
ExternalSyncDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the NullableDateTime the item was last synched NullableDateTime
ExternalType Gets or sets the integer type of external integration integer
ExternalUpdatedBy Gets or sets the string external user who last updated the item string
FullTextFieldUpdatedDateTimeUTC Gets or sets the NullableDateTime one of the full text indexed fields were updated for the item. NullableDateTime
HasIntegrationObject Gets the boolean indicator that this item is a synchronized external object. boolean
HideForLimitedView Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the item is hidden from view boolean
Id guid
IntegrationDirectoryObject Gets the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.IntegrationDirectoryObject for this object if it is an External Item. RestDirectoryObject
IntegrationExternalObjects Gets the Collection of Object of DomainIntegrationExternalObject objects related this object. Collection of Object
IsActive Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating that the item is Active.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
IsActiveDescription Gets the string description if the current is active state string
IsApproved Gets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the item is approved by the related approval. boolean
IsDescriptionHtml Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the description is HTML. boolean
IsDisableForcePermissions Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the item will not accept force permissions settings from container items. Default false. boolean
IsDisplayAllContentsInNavigation Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not a new direct item child will have the ProjectInsight.Items.ItemBase.IsDisplayedInNavigation turned on when created. Defaults to false. boolean
IsDisplayedInNavigation Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the item is displayed in the navigation. Default false. boolean
IsDisplaySearch Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the search appears when using "List" or "PageSpanList" display type. boolean
IsDisplaySearchStartCharacter Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the start character search picker appears when using "List" or "PageSpanList" display type. boolean
IsForcePermissionSettingsOnChildren Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the permissions settings need to be forced on the children during permissions changes. boolean
IsInheritablePermissions Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not the item inherits permissions from it"s container. Default true. boolean
IsItemCommentSystemEnabled Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating whether or not system comments are enabled for the item\, which is calculated on the related domain. boolean
IsMasterFolder Gets or sets the boolean flag indicating the folder is a master folder. (Only applies to folders) boolean
IsObjectCreated Gets or sets the boolean flag which determines whether or not the current object has just been created (is new) and will need to be saved to the database. The property is marked new so that each layer of the inheritence chain has it"s own IsObjectCreated property. The IsObjectCreated flag is automatically set to false when the object is saved. Base layers may or may not be created. The IsObjectCreated flag is set to false when saved. boolean
IsObjectDirty Gets or sets the boolean flag which determines whether or not the current object has been updated and needs to be saved to the database. The property is marked new so that each layer of the inheritence chain has it"s own IsObjectDirty property. Base layers may or may not be dirty. The IsObjectDirty flag should set to true when a property is updated\, and the object automatically sets the IsObjectDirty flag to false when the object is saved successfully. The IsObjectDirty property is used primarly for the internal Save methods to determine whether or not the object needs to save itself when the Save method is invoked. boolean
IsObjectLoaded Gets or sets the boolean flag which determines whether or not the current object has been loaded from the database.
